Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!

Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Black Magician User,\N Pandora"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What bullshit are you trying to pull on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That shitty card can't even compare to the rareness of my card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}B-But you agreed to this Ante before we started the duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I changed my mind!\NThe loser has to obey as the winner tells him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-No way... come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who's this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm the Battle City Steering Committee Chairman, Mokuba Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my job to settle trouble relating to all tournament matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't screw around with my rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Someone who doesn't abide by the rules has no right to call himself a duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a poor duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Seto Kaiba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When you insult my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's no different than directly insulting Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I assume you're prepared for the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What'd you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A-Amazing...! These are all rare cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm challenging you to a duel right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, the condition is that you take all the rare cards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you like from this case and rebuild your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll regret that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once I claim your rare cards, I'll have the best deck around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cards are power! There's a 100% chance of you losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go! Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll show you God. This is what true power is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}God is in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Two cards left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When I find the two in this city...\NI will own a deck equal to God himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi... I'll wait for you on this road of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You found the owner of {\c&HD29F2C&}Obelisk{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. Domino City, North C Block.\NThe owner of {\c&HD29F2C&}Obelisk{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But how did Kaiba get hold of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can imagine... He hosted this tournament because he got his hands on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}His purpose is to unify the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, it was you, wasn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Open the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Malik, my Millennium Tauk warned me you would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For 3,000 years, our tribe has sworn to protect the King's tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you intend to defy them by doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sacrifice myself for what?!\NSomeone has to break them of this myth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once I obtain all three God Cards, I'll gain right to the Pharaoh's title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And our tribe can be freed from this curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's betraying our tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I cannot let you pass here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Move and let me pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you really use your Millennium Rod against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it's for the sake of our future, then I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if it's you, Dear sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dear sister, it was you who had the last card, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You must have foreseen the future with your Millennium Tauk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You gave Seto Kaiba the {\c&HD29F2C&}Obelisk{\r} card...\NThen he held this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You knew that, by the god's guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my fate and his would eventually intertwine in Domino City.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:07:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But in the end, the final God Card...\NWill fall into my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Along with the title of Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kaiba is still in the North Block.\NShall I assemble a team to attack him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, let Kaiba be for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I finally found Pharaoh after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Assemble Pandora the Conjurer, for a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then, I'll be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm a bit worried about Yugi and Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Honda-san...\NI have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was wondering if you could take me to Domino City on the day I get my bandages taken off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take you to Domino City?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah. I want to see Big brother dueling with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shizuka-chan will have her bandages taken off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to try hard for Shizuka-chan, my disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:07:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to look for Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Partner... This card we're holding for him is Jounouchi-kun's courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}You mean Jounouchi-kun's fighting in order to get his card back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}I'm sure Jounouchi-kun will survive Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}Yeah. When that time comes, I'll surely accept his challenge. The duelist Jounouchi Katsuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}It doesn't matter which of us wins or loses.\NIt'll be a good memory for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}Just like the memories of playing games with Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,100)}That's right... You don't have any memories from before you met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rare Hunter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're telling me to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, that's Yugi, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where'd you go, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, answer us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Big brother, the portable tracking computer said Mutou Yugi's signal disappeared from the tracking screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mokuba! Try to locate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Duel Disks should keep a constant signal of every duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If the signal is not being read, Yugi might be inside a building that's blocking the signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For example, a basement or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My duelist data...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}I've been waiting for you, Yugi.\NMy master, the great Pandora-sama, will duel you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pandora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}I'll show you there is only one true user of the Magician {\fnMagician\c&H9F026D&\3c&H01B451&}Spellcaster{\r}{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}-type monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Pandora-sama, the Conjurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop the petty tricks and come on out!\NRare Hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome. I am the second Rare Hunter, Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also known as the Conjurer, and user of the {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome. I am the second Rare Hunter, Pandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also known as the Conjurer, and user of the {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}User of the {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, I'm aware you often use the {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} to defeat your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I am the master of Magicians!\NThere's no one who can defeat my {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duelists choose the cards the trust most\N out of a very large amount of cards, this building their deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But sometimes the cards choose the duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the hearts of both the cards and the duelist become one,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the cards' true power can be unleashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rare Hunters don't have the duelists' heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll take you on, Pandora!\NMy {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I expected. You're said to accept any duel. It seems no different with me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now then, this room is a bit crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've prepared a special duel ring for us... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The truth is, Malik-sama informed me you would be in this very area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Malik?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A Millennium Item wielder, and the leader of Ghouls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is he right now?!\NAnswer me, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who knows? Where ever could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's {\i1}very{\i0} close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You might say, he's in {\i1}here{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Malik has the power to take control of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Could it be this Pandora is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now then, please enter.\NThis will be our duel ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pandora's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cards have often been used here during special occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, this is the perfect stage for the new {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}'s duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The solid vision system can be used here.\NBut Kaiba Corporation can't locate us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now then, let us get started.\NWe'll each shuffle our own decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The way you cut and shuffle, you'll damage your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm used to doing it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's an old saying among gamblers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Trust your friends, but always cut the cards."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Friends"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no way I'd call you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, now that we are committed to Dueling,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd like to show you something that will prove we are truly {\i1}blood{\i0} brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Nightmare Show will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I am cuffed as well.\NNow the both of us can't escape from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will now show you the greatest show in history
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}as I, "Pandora the Conjurer", escape from the very jaws of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a 100-tooth carbide tipped saw you see in magic shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you understand the rules of this duel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The saws are aligned along a set of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Life Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The closer they get to 0, the closer the blade gets to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's correct! It's a nightmare game where the loser's body will be sawed apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Furthermore, please take a look at your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This contains the final hope of both you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This box...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Within this box lies the key that will open the shackles at our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It can only be opened when the opposite player's Life Points reaches 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In other words, only the winner can escape from here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pandora's Box...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Greek god Zeus created a box containing all the misfortune in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the moment a woman sharing the name opened it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}all the evil escaped, bringing about evil, suffering and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, a tiny bit of hope was left at the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The very key at the bottom of this box is our last hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this {\i1}fun{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A battle with people's {\i1}lives{\i0} on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm asking you if you think it's {\i1}fun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. Because {\i1}I{\i0} will be the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You filthy {\i1}scum{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'll show you what a true duelist's fight looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Draw 5 cards from your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} is already within my hand, as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was simple to ensure this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a certain technique designed to let me draw the cards I need most.\NThis allows me to add certain cards to my hand from the start of the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This technique goes by the name 'Stripper'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All I had to do was cut specific cards so they are slightly smaller than the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I cut the three {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}s in my deck like this... And when you cut the deck, {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} will surely be at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi, I'll teach you what it's like facing a card trickster like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In this death game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here I go! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I set a card on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, {\c&H3896AE&}Magnet Warrior Alpha{\r} in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H3896AE&}Legion of Fiend Jester{\r} in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just need one more monster to Sacrifice Summon, and I can Summon {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} to the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pandora, I'm going to play a Magic Card this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an1}Magic Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And that card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H36A637&}Hand Obliteration{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wh-What!? {\c&H36A637&}Hand Obliteration{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now both players' hands are destroyed!\NThat includes you, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Destroy our hands...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Discard it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, you have {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} in your hand already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Of course I'd not drop my guard around a trickster like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Judging by the way you cut and shuffle, you don't seem to cherish your cards at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It doesn't surprise me you'd cut them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C-Could it be you were aware of my trick from the start?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My turn's not over yet!\NSet card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H36A637&}Brain Control{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H36A637&}Brain Control{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's going to take control of my monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I sacrifice {\c&H3896AE&}Magnet Warrior Alpha{\r} and {\c&H3896AE&}Legion of Fiend Jester{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I Summon {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll show you the anger of the cards, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He was able to Summon his {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} before I played mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were the one who set up such a dangerous game. But I assume you're prepared to suffer because of that, Pandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}! Direct Attack the player!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The attack just now cut your Life Points in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now then! Show me how tough you are facing your own rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He got the best of me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But the real show's just starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\pos(128,130)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a battle of {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r} VS {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But in order to win, Pandora offers to take the soul of his own monster, and put Yugi in a great pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yugi believes in his cards until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please, {\c&H3896AE&}Black Magician{\r}!\NAnswer Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next time: "Soul Black Magic"\NDuel standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.33,0:23:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
